title: Learn to Paint: Warhammer 40,000 - Termagants and Ripper Swarm + Paints Set
description:
This set includes everything you need to get some terrifying looking Termagants and a Ripper Swarm painted and ready to devour your enemies on the gaming table in no time. Follow this step-by-step guide to learn how to paint these hungry miniatures with just the contents of the box set, in the colours of Hive Fleet Leviathan. 
 .
If you're new to painting - check out our Citadel Colour Painting Essentials videos to learn all about it.

You can learn more about the game here: https://bit.ly/3ryNxde

title: Learn to Paint: Warhammer 40,000 - Infernus Marines + Paints Set
description:
This set includes everything you need to get some awesome looking Infernus Marines painted and onto the gaming table in no time. Follow this step-by-step guide to learn how to paint these fiery miniatures with just the contents of the box set in the colours of the courageous Ultramarines!  

If you're new to painting - check out our Citadel Colour Painting Essentials videos to learn all about it.

You can learn more about the game here: https://bit.ly/3ryNxde
